ETS APCJ  Extension DEV for delivering AP Chinese and Japanese exams to students on Chromebooks.
The app can be accessed using credentials provided to students on test day. 
The test app is launched as a kiosk app for enhanced security. Students are restricted from accessing other applications while taking the assessment.
